        "subject": "LU-18687 build: replace autotools dist with git archive",
        "message": "LU-18687 build: replace autotools dist with git archive\n\nAutotools automatically creates a dist make target to\ngenerate the tarball for Lustre. This requires a large\namount of Makefile boilerplate. Instead, use git archive\nto override the autotools implementation.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: I354ac7f23956c007475c9787741875c9ad5059dd\n"
      },
